---
description: Use published icon packs for brand logos; no hand-authored brand SVGs
alwaysApply: true
---

# Brand logos and provider marks

For third-party brand marks (Google, Apple, OAuth/social providers, app stores, etc.), import from a maintained open-source set—for example **`react-icons`** (`react-icons/fc`, `react-icons/si`, and other subpaths) or another established package.

Do **not** paste or maintain custom inline SVG `<path>` data for those brands in app components unless taken verbatim from a linked, vendor-approved asset workflow the team owns.
